              "name": "ob6P1",
              "fill": "#3F3F46",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "LazyAudio 让你能录下电脑系统音和麦克风。在大多数国家和地区，你录自己的声音、自己的会议没有问题。但有些地方对录制他人的声音有更严格的规定（如美国部分州的 two-party consent 法律）。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "dIdvP",
              "name": "ob6P2",
              "fill": "#18181B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "在录制对方音频之前，请遵守当地法律，并按需告知对方。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "SjMYN",
              "name": "ob6P3",
              "fill": "#3F3F46",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "LazyAudio 不会上传你的录音 — 但你与他人分享录音 / 转录时，请同样注意对方的同意权。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
